  "title": "A Fair and Responsible Delivery Service",
  "article_text": "Our company has a primary goal: to deliver packages quickly and carefully. We collect items from your home or office, and we inform you about the delivery time by video call. The weather can affect the flow of our work, so we must be flexible. Our drivers are highly trained and absolutely responsible for every package. They must not show any sex discrimination, and they treat every customer with fairness. The principle of our service is simple: we build trust through good work. We also offer additional services, like a flat rate for heavy boxes. The appeal of our service is clear, because we always try to be fair. We use a direct connection to update customers about their packages in real time. This trial showed that a straight approach and honest communication reduce stress for everyone.",
